\ls2\ilvl1\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	
\f1 \uc0\u9702 
\f0 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
Additionally, while a piece of knowledge expressed by words in a biography, like 'Henry had 4 brothers', it has to be inferred from others statements in the linked data language (for example counting the number of 'brother of').\
